+modal('jitera-boost', "Jitera Boost")
  p Jitera Boost is the AI agent runtime at the core of Jitera's platform. Built on my open-source project Harbor, it provides a modular workflow engine for LLM-powered agents — handling tool calls, memory, context retrieval, streaming responses, and multi-step task execution.
  p I led its development throughout my time at Jitera, evolving it from a prototype into a production system serving enterprise clients with thousands of daily interactions.
  p Key capabilities included: a module system for composing agent behaviors, a structured memory/context engine, Python sandbox execution, MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration, and support for long-running agentic tasks.
  ul
    li
      a(href="https://github.com/av/harbor") Harbor on GitHub
